thumb.title: Cefali & Cefali Personal Injury Lawyers
thumb.description: Cefali & Cefali are personal injury attorneys located in Contra Costa County, California, specifically in the city of Pleasant Hill, CA. The firm handles every kind of personal injury case including car accidents, trucking accidents, bicycle accidents, motorcycle accidents, boating accidents, pedestrian accidents, rideshare accidents, slip and fall cases, whiplash injuries, dog bite injuries, accidents involving brain injuries, assault and battery injuries, and accidents involving DUI or DWI. The law firm is pleased to help the people of Contra Costa County, CA and the cities within Contra Costa County such as Pleasant Hill, Martinez, Concord, Antioch, Walnut Creek, Richmond, Brentwood, Pittsburg, San Ramon, San Pablo, Danville, El Cerrito.Cefali & Cefali Personal Injury Lawyers2800 Pleasant Hill Rd ste 100, Pleasant Hill, CA 94523, United States949-325-7790https://callcefali.com/pleasant-hill-personal-injury-lawyer/
